title: Judas Priest - 1988 - Ram It Down [320kbs] ~~Renovatio~~
description:
Ram It Down is the eleventh studio album by Judas Priest, released in 1988 through Columbia Records; a remastered edition containing two bonus tracks was reissued in 2001. The album earned gold certification (500,000 sales) on 18 July 1988. The band toured in Europe and North America to support the release of the album. This is the last album to feature long time drummer Dave Holland and the last studio album produced by long-time collaborator Tom Allom
